ned in pkg/kubelet/configmap/configmap_manager.go (lines 148-153) for ConfigMaps and pkg/kubelet/secret/secret_manager.go (lines 149-154) for Secrets. These implementations are used by NewWatchingConfigMapManager (line 138) and NewWatchingSecretManager (line 139) to create watch-based managers that optimize resource usage by stopping watches on immutable objects."
